data.title: Birds at Lagunas de Espera Spain birding sites
data.text:
Tucked away in a quiet bit of countryside, this is a delightful spot with 3 attractive lakes. White-headed Duck and Purple Gallinule should be easy to find. I had Red-knobbed Coot and Little Bittern as well and Marbled Duck and Ferruginous Duck also occur here. However, you get much better views at Laguna de Medina, for example.
